        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-night",
      "startTime": 18.1666664584
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-night",
      "startTime": 18.1666664584
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "改めてお疲れ様\n最高のステージだったぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Once again‚ great job.\nIt was an amazing performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.9999998553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます、{user}さん！\n全力で夏を満喫しました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ {user}-san!\nI enjoyed summer to the fullest!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.0343533341,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-night",
      "startTime": 29.0343532149
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "同人誌即売会っていうのにも初めて行ったし\nステージも全力を出し切ったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was my first time at a fanzine convention‚\nand I gave my all on stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.2676866674,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "もうへとへとですよ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm completely exhausted!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.9010198815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-night",
      "startTime": 39.1010198815
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、三人ともよく頑張ったな\n解散の前に、軽く明日の予定だけ伝えておくよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ all three of you did really well.\nBefore we call it a day‚ let me quickly go over tomorrow's schedule.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.4333331887,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "明日は午後から、今回のステージ衣装で\nグラビア撮影だ。午前中はゆっくり休んでくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tomorrow afternoon‚ we'll be doing a photoshoot\nin the stage outfits from today. You can rest up in the morning.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.966666522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-night",
      "startTime": 52.9460987949
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "え……？　{user}さん\nじゃあ明日の午前中は……オフ、ってことですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait… {user}-san‚ does that mean…\nWe have the morning off tomorrow!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.5460989141,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-night",
      "startTime": 62.6127654616
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "明日の午前中は、オフ……\nオフ……予定が、ない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The tomorrow morning off…\nOff… No plans…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.6794322474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみれ？　何かまずかったか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Su-Sumire? Is something wrong…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.3794321282,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-night",
      "startTime": 75.8856450621
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、いえっ！\n大丈夫です、全然問題ありません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ n-no!\nIt's totally fine‚ no problem at all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.0107037545,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-night",
      "startTime": 80.0856450621
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか……よし\nとりあえず、ホテルに移動しよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-Okay… good.\nAnyway‚ let's head back to the hotel.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.985645221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.8665987792
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.8665987792
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "荷物、運んでくれてありがとうございます\n瑠依ちゃんと優ちゃん、すっごく眠そうでしたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for carrying the luggage.\nRui-chan and Yu-chan looked really sleepy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.3332669718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.0999319934
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "同人誌即売会に、新曲の準備……\n最近忙しかったからな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They've been busy with the fanzine sale and preparing for the new song…\nThey've been really busy lately…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.9999336385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "明日も午前中はゆっくり休むって言ってたしな\nすみれも疲れてるだろうし、のんびり過ごしてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They said they'll rest in the morning tomorrow as well.\nSumire‚ you're probably tired too‚ so take it easy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.3666695738,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.978503313
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "……あの～、そういえば、{user}さん\nここ、すっごく海が近いですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Um‚ by the way‚ {user}-san‚\nThis place is really close to the sea‚ isn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.3785049581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　あぁ、そうだな\n部屋の窓からビーチが見渡せるくらいだしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm? Oh‚ yeah‚ it is.\nYou can see the beach from the room's window.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.2000029071,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.5719272835
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "後、スタッフさんに聞いたんですが～……\nビーチに並んでた屋台、明日まで出てるそうです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I heard from the staff…\nThe stalls lined up on the beach will be there until tomorrow!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.1719289286,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.3052606169
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "焼きそば、かき氷、焼きとうもろこし……\nすっごく美味しそうでしたよね！　ね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yakisoba‚ shaved ice‚ grilled corn…\nThey all looked really delicious‚ didn't they? Right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.8938221616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そういえばあったなぁ……\n何か食べたいものがあったなら明日買ってこようか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that you mention it…\nIf there's something you want to eat‚ I can buy it for you tomorrow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.0666695738,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.7219045543
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "そんな！　{user}さんに悪いですよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No way! I'd feel bad making you do that‚ {user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.7219045543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.2552409394
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_07_01-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "でも～……めずらしい味のかき氷はありましたね！\nレインボー白玉あんこスペシャル……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… there was that unusual flavored shaved ice!\nThe Rainbow Shiratama Red Beans Special…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.4219092512,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
